OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784296099
OL,3,CMan, 82, suffered brain damage in road
OL,4,Crage attack on supermarket trip
OL,6,FA driver who left an 82-year-old man
OL,7,Fneeding round-the-clock care after a
OL,8,Froad rage attack has been jailed for
OL,9,F12 years.
OL,11,FLee Symonds, 42, repeatedly punched
OL,12,FJohn Knowles before slamming his head
OL,13,Fin his car door during the incident
OL,14,Fnear Skipton, North Yorkshire.
OL,16,FMr Knowles, who had been driving to
OL,17,Fthe supermarket, suffered life-
OL,18,Fchanging injuries.
OL,20,FIn a statement his family said he will
OL,21,F"never be the same again".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
