FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784296099
OL,3,CMan, 82, suffered brain damage in road
OL,4,Crage attack on supermarket trip
OL,6,FSymonds, of Greatwood Avenue, Skipton,
OL,7,Fwas jailed at Bradford Crown Court
OL,8,Fafter admitting dangerous driving and
OL,9,Fcausing grievous bodily harm with
OL,10,Fintent.
OL,12,FThe court heard Mr Knowles was
OL,13,Ftravelling along Broughton Road when
OL,14,Fhe pulled out of a junction onto the
OL,15,FA59 at Carleton on 4 August 2023.
OL,17,FSymonds, who was following in his car,
OL,18,Fdrove alongside and tried to force Mr
OL,19,FKnowles off the road.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784296099
OL,3,CMan, 82, suffered brain damage in road
OL,4,Crage attack on supermarket trip
OL,6,FHe then pulled in front of Mr Knowles'
OL,7,Fcar and braked sharply, causing a
OL,8,Fcollision.
OL,10,FAfter both men got out of their cars,
OL,11,FSymonds launched his attack, causing
OL,12,FMr Knowles to slump against his
OL,13,Fvehicle before "using the car door as
OL,14,Fa weapon", North Yorkshire Police said.
OL,16,FSymonds fled after witnesses
OL,17,Fintervened.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784296099
OL,3,CMan, 82, suffered brain damage in road
OL,4,Crage attack on supermarket trip
OL,6,FMr Knowles suffered multiple fractures
OL,7,Fto his eye and cheek bone, a displaced
OL,8,Ftooth and nerve damage, which left him
OL,9,Funable to eat for 10 days and required
OL,10,F24-hour care from his family.
OL,12,FHe suffered two bleeds on the brain
OL,13,Fwhich needed surgery.
OL,15,FMr Knowles' family said they "became
OL,16,Fcarers overnight, working shifts to
OL,17,Fstay with him".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784296099
OL,3,CMan, 82, suffered brain damage in road
OL,4,Crage attack on supermarket trip
OL,6,FIn a statement they said: "All of that
OL,7,Fwas almost three years ago now and
OL,8,Fwriting this today, it is still
OL,9,Fdifficult to comprehend that he was
OL,10,Fsubjected to such a savage road rage
OL,11,Fattack resulting in life changing
OL,12,Fconsequences that we, as a family,
OL,13,Fcontinue to experience on a daily
OL,14,Fbasis.
OL,16,F"The outcome for dad has been that
OL,17,Fyes, he survived, but his quality of
OL,18,Flife changed for the worse and he will
OL,19,Fnever get that back.
OL,26,@nD@[OUxD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784296099
OL,3,CMan, 82, suffered brain damage in road
OL,4,Crage attack on supermarket trip
OL,6,F"We have come to accept that,
OL,7,Frealistically, he will never be the
OL,8,Fsame again now."
OL,10,FThey told Symonds: "You robbed a
OL,11,Fvulnerable, elderly man of precious
OL,12,Fquality time in the twilight of his
OL,13,Fyears. You took away his confidence,
OL,14,Fhis independence, his freedom and his
OL,15,Fdignity."
OL,17,FNorth Yorkshire Police investigator
OL,18,FLorraine Whipp praised the family's
OL,19,F"strength and resilience".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@TOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
