PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784296099
OL,3,CMan, 82, suffered brain damage in road
OL,4,Crage attack on supermarket trip
OL,6,FShe added: "This was an horrific and
OL,7,Funprovoked attack that subjected Mr
OL,8,FKnowles and his family to years of
OL,9,Fongoing trauma."
OL,26,@nD@LOU
